name: Progresso / Progress in a Plastic Bag
description: O que é viver no Brasil pandêmico? Somos mercadorias ou pessoas? *** Pedro Surubim (@osurubim) performs his impressions to the most asked questions in his country today: what is it like to live in pandemic Brazil? Are we goods or people?  Fascism in Brazil is blocking our air, and our freedom is like being in a plastic bag.
